=\"card-img-top\" alt=\"野球部\">\n<div class=\"card-body\">\n<h3 class=\"card-title h5\">野球部</h3>\n<p class=\"card-text link-primary\">野球部が主催した「KCSソフトボール大会」</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"col\">\n<div class=\"card h-100 shadow\">\n<img src=\"images/photo_p12.jpg\" class=\"card-img-top\" alt=\"リフレッシュルーム\">\n<div class=\"card-body\">\n<h3 class=\"card-title h5\">リフレッシュルーム</h3>\n<p class=\"card-text\">ホッとリラックスタイム</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"col\">\n<a href=\"../journal/2025/12_festival.html\">\n<div class=\"card h-100 shadow\">\n<img src=\"../journal/2025/images/12_festival_p01.webp\" class=\"card-img-top\" alt=\"KCS文化祭\">\n<div class=\"card-body\">\n<h3 class=\"card-title h5\">KCS文化祭</h3>\n<p class=\"card-text link-primary\">サブカルチャーにスポットを当てたイベント</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"col\">\n<a href=\"../journal/2024/12_illumination.html\">\n<div class=\"card h-100 shadow\">\n<img src=\"../journal/2024/images/12_illumination_p01.webp\" class=\"card-img-top\" alt=\"冬のファンタジー\">\n<div class=\"card-body\">\n<h3 class=\"card-title h5\">冬のファンタジー<small>（12月）</small></h3>\n<p class=\"card-text link-primary\">心温まるイルミネーション、見に来てね</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n</div>\n\n</div><!-- /.row -->\n</div><!-- /.container-fluid -->\n\n</main>\n<!-- InstanceEndEditable -->\n\n<p id=\"pagetop\"><a href=\"#header\"><i class=\"bi bi-arrow-bar-up fs-4\"></i></a></p>\n<div id=\"footer\"></div>\n<script src=\"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.min.js\" integrity=\"sha256-/JqT3SQfawRcv/BIHPThkBvs0OEvtFFmqPF/lYI/Cxo=\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>\n<script src=\"../js/default02.js\"></script> \n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js\" integrity=\"sha384-geWF76RCwLtnZ8qwWowPQNguL3RmwHVBC9FhGdlKrxdiJJigb/j/68SIy3Te4Bkz\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css\">\n<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cl